Package com.financial.statistical_analysis

Class StatisticalExpenses

java.lang.Object
com.financial.statistical_analysis.StatisticalExpenses
public class StatisticalExpenses extends Object
Utility class for performing statistical analysis on entity expenditures.

Leverages the Apache Commons Math library to compute descriptive statistics and provides specialized algorithms for financial anomaly detection.
